import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Stack, Link, Box, Divider, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import { Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn } from '@mui/icons-material';
import { blue, grey } from '@mui/material/colors';

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#0A0A0A', color: grey[300], padding: '20px 0' }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Stack spacing={3} alignItems="center">
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: blue[500] }}>
            SportsZone
          </Typography>
          <Stack direction="row" spacing={2}>
            <Link href="https://www.facebook.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <IconButton color="inherit">
                <Facebook />
              </IconButton>
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://www.twitter.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <IconButton color="inherit">
                <Twitter />
              </IconButton>
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://www.instagram.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <IconButton color="inherit">
                <Instagram />
              </IconButton>
            </Link>
            <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com" color="inherit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <IconButton color="inherit">
                <LinkedIn />
              </IconButton>
            </Link>
          </Stack>
          <Divider sx={{ width: '100%', backgroundColor: grey[700] }} />
          <Typography variant="body2" align="center">
            Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} SportsZone. All rights reserved.
          </Typography>
          <Stack direction="row" spacing={3} sx={{ justifyContent: 'center' }}>
            <Link href="/privacy-policy" color="inherit">
              Privacy Policy
            </Link>
            <Link href="/terms-of-service" color="inherit">
              Terms of Service
            </Link>
            <Link href="/contact-us" color="inherit">
              Contact Us
            </Link>
          </Stack>
        </Stack>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
